data.description: SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE $10,000 TOWARDS  BUYERSCLOSING COSTS ON FULL PRICE OFFER! SUBMIT YOUR OFFER TODAY! Welcome Home! Or to your vacation home away from home ! Or to your next income producing investment! Whether you're a first time home buyer or a seasoned investor this home is awaiting you! This charming 3 bedroom 1 bathroom home sits on almost a quarter acre lot, lots of space to play with and includes a large pool with working Pump. New laminate flooring in the bedrooms (2020) , New paint inside and out (2023), New AC Pump (2021) New Pool Pump (2020/2021)The house is within the Cocoa city limits. It's about a 25 minute drive to cocoa beach, Orlando is about a 45 minute drive , and only about a 8 minute drive from the Historic Cocoa Village, where you can enjoy from all different shops, restaurants, water view and local activities. This area is growing, lots of new developments nearby, this is great deal! NO HOA so take advantage and come add your own touch to this home and make it your next big move! Call today for a showing!!
